textDelta: Where is the UN located ? The United Nations is headquartered in New York City.
Where is the real UN power located ? The real UN power is located in the Security Council.
Where is wavelength found ? Wavelength is found in the electromagnetic spectrum.
Where in the spectrum is wavelength found ? Wavelength is found in the visible spectrum.

What does additional protein cause ? The body's natural response to additional protein intake is an increase in the production of insulin-like growth factor 1 (IGF-1). This hormone is responsible for the growth and repair of muscle tissue.
What does the skeletal muscle tissue do ? The skeletal muscle tissue contracts to produce movement.
What is the function of the skeletal muscle ? The skeletal muscle is responsible for the movement of the bones.

Who said " Peace, commerce and honest friendship with all nations entangling alliances with none ? This quote is often attributed to George Washington, but there is no evidence that he actually said it.
Who said " Peace, commerce and honest friendship with all nations entangling alliances with none ? Thomas Jefferson
